  <h2>Innovative diagnostics</h2>
  <p>We are the preferred partner for the public and private sectors for innovative diagnostics. Through continuous research and collaboration with universities and the pharmaceutical industry, we can make new tests available to the medical community at an early stage.</p>

  <p>Our research focuses on genetics, women's health, cardiology, nutrigenomics and others. At the same time, we are constantly improving our IT solutions and services. We use PathProvider as our electronic results platform, so you can access your results on the go as soon as they become available in the lab.</p>

  <p>We are committed to developing personalised medicine, and one area of personalised medicine that we focus on is pharmacogenetics. The efficacy of a drug is highly dependent on the genetic variations of patients. Therapies are becoming more sophisticated, but at the same time, they are becoming more individualised. One advanced field in this area of medicine is companion diagnostics.</p>

  <p>Companion diagnostics refers to diagnostics created in parallel with drug development, which enables physicians to make better decisions about drug efficacy and dosage.</p>

  <p>We have entered this diagnostics area to provide physicians with the latest and most innovative service offerings.</p>

  

